#PROJECT OVERVIEW
Redirective is a microservice that redirects users to the correct page based on the tracking link redirect rules.
Each tracking link has a unique slug which is used to identify the redirect rule and final destination URL template.
Redirect results in a new Click record being created and processed by numerous handlers (interactor.ClickHandlerInterface).

